ABUJA – Abuja Newspapers Distributors, under the aegis of Abuja Newspapers Distributors Association (ANDA), have felicitated with the Speaker of the House of Representatives, Rt. Hon. Femi Gbajabiamila, on his 60th birth anniversary. The Speaker celebrates his birthday on every June 25. In a statement released and signed by the President of the Association, Comr. Benji Obute on Saturday, the Association said Gbajabiamila had written his name in the gold considering the love he had shown towards them. Benji said the visit of the Speaker to the newspapers distribution center in Abuja in 2020, the first of its kind by any high-ranking public officer, remained a reference point in the anal of history of the Association. The statement added that as friend of newspapers distributors in Abuja, the Speaker would always be celebrated by them. The statement reads in part; “Members of Abuja Newspapers Distributors Association (ANDA) felicitate with the Speaker of all Speakers, the Speaker of the 9th NASS, on his 60th birthday. “Sir, we appreciate your leadership prowess and pray to Almighty God to grant you many more glorious and prosperous years ahead.”